{
  "texts": [
    "We introduced SGFE, an effective feature extraction method capable of capturing molecular and structural features of drug atoms and important substructures.",
    "In the context of DDI prediction, we integrated drug sequence information and drug molecular graph structural information, enabling the capture of a broader range of feature information for enhanced DDI prediction accuracy.",
    "The case studies demonstrate that SSF-DDI can recognize drug-drug interactions (DDIs) in novel scenarios beyond the dataset.",
    "Moreover, SSF-DDI is capable of identifying significant substructure information related to DDIs.",
    "The accurate prediction of drug interactions has significant implications in multiple domains and holds considerable application value."
  ]
}